title: Levi's Women's 711 Super Skinny Jeans
description: LEVI'S 711: These jeans are designed to flatter, hold and lift for the ultimate versatile look-amazing jeans.
SIZE & FIT: These 711 jeans have a mid rise and skinny leg that fits slim through the hip and thigh, designed to hug your curves. Inseams: Short = 28; Regular = 30; Long = 32
MATERIAL & FABRIC: Levi's 711 jeans are made from a cotton blend.
CARE INSTRUCTIONS: Machine wash cold inside out with like colors, Do not bleach, Tumble dry medium, Hot iron if needed, Dry cleaning possible.

Levi's signature 'Lot 700' fits are the ultimate look-amazing jeans, designed to flatter, hold and lift. An ultra-sleek silhouette that hugs and celebrates your figure. Finished with the skinniest leg in the Levi's collection. Made with Levi's Sculpt with Hyperstretch, an advanced blend of Lycra and cotton fibers for extreme stretch.
